Class ApiControllerContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.actioncontroller.ApiControllerContext
  • public class ApiControllerContext
extends Object
    Extra initialization variables for the ActionControllers. Attributes can be set on an ApiServlet or ApiHandler and read by HttpParameterMapperFactory.create(ANNOTATION, java.lang.reflect.Parameter, org.actioncontroller.ApiControllerContext)
